1
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,760
In the winter of the tenth year of Kaiyuan,

2
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:05,480
the Anlan Dam in Dongshui Town, Yangzhou collapsed.

3
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,560
The flood drowned the people,

4
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,720
and countless commoners lost their lives.

5
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:10,800
To pacify the disaster, His Majesty

6
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,280
not only donated money for relief,

7
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:15,400
but also gave the state-protecting glazed orb, which symbolizes peace and harmony,

8
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,130
to Kaiyuan Temple in Yangzhou.

9
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:20,640
This orb was transported from Chang'an to Yangzhou,

10
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:22,800
but vanished without a trace in Luoyang.

11
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,040
Minister of Revenue Lu Yunxian

12
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:26,370
was dismissed along with other officials

13
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,800
and imprisoned.

14
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:31,040
Minister Lu is my uncle.

15
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,600
He treated me very well when I was young.

16
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:35,200
If the orb can be found,

17
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:38,480
I will definitely be able to save my uncle from prison.

18
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:43,240
Who escorted the precious pearl along the way?

19
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:47,079
It was relayed by transport commissioners from each post station, appointed by Minister Lu.

20
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:49,040
There were seven post stations in total.

21
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:51,120
Each station had three transport commissioners.

22
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:53,320
The precious pearl was placed in a chest

23
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:56,000
and handed over sequentially through the post stations.

24
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,320
It departed from Chang'an,

25
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,720
heading to Luoyang and Bianzhou Pavilion.

26
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:02,320
But the envoy's transport cart never arrived,

27
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,440
so they knew something went wrong.

28
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:07,800
The government has been tracking the whereabouts of the pearl.

29
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,480
However, the pearl never appeared again.

30
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,680
It became a cold case.

31
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:16,000
We recently caught a transport commissioner.

32
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,329
Here is the confession.

33
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:30,440
Here, take a look first.

34
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,520
Okay.

35
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,960
Stop.

36
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:58,840
Did you steal the pearl?

37
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:02,120
Even if you gave me a hundred times the courage,

38
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:04,680
I wouldn't dare steal what I was guarding.

39
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:11,000
The three of us received the goods at the Luoyang post station,

40
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:14,200
and immediately headed to the Bianzhou post station.

41
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:18,160
Who knew that while passing Niutou Mountain,

42
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:21,160
we suddenly heard cries for help.

43
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:25,280
It turned out to be two traveling merchants attacked by bandits.

44
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:29,340
and robbed them of all their valuable gold and silver jewelry.

45
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:42,320
At that time, we were too soft-hearted,

46
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:45,480
so we dismounted to check their carriage.

47
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:51,000
They took advantage of our unpreparedness

48
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,920
and threw knockout powder at us.

49
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,880
By the time I woke up,

50
00:04:57,440 --> 00:05:00,370
the treasure we were transporting was already gone.

51
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,920
Wake up.

52
00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:10,720
Wake up.

53
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:14,280
We three brothers all knew

54
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:17,400
that losing the transported goods would surely cost us our heads.

55
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:19,160
We simply made up our minds

56
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,520
and fled for our lives.

57
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,840
We changed our names

58
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:24,400
and lived in seclusion.

59
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,360
Where are they?

60
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:39,400
We swore an oath

61
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:42,120
to never contact each other again.

62
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,920
Could it be

63
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:50,720
a trap they set on purpose?

64
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:55,240
There were plenty of opportunities along the way.

65
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:57,200
Why collude with outsiders?

66
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,500
What did that merchant look like?

67
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,530
Any distinguishing features?

68
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:09,040
He had a scar on his face.

69
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:11,400
I know him.

70
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,080
His name is Moya,

71
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:17,130
and he has a daughter named Moying.

72
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:19,360
They make a living by stealing.

73
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:21,080
The local yamen has wanted them for a long time,

74
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:23,040
but hasn't caught them yet.

75
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,680
On the Ghost Festival,

76
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:27,320
Su Lang and I found their whereabouts

77
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,560
and chased them all the way.

78
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:30,280
I saw his face.

79
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:33,240
There is a long scar on the left side.

80
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:36,600
That was the day you bumped me out of the coffin.

81
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,360
Come, let me take a look.

82
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:45,240
I know this person too.

83
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,680
You know him too?

84
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,400
I personally convicted him.

85
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,600
He wasn't called Moya back then,

86
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:54,280
but Zhang Shuijing.

87
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,000
How come I didn't know?

88
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,440
I've never heard you mention it.

89
00:06:57,440 --> 00:07:00,120
You were still in your mother's womb at that time.

90
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,680
Chen You was the magistrate,

91
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:03,680
and I was the recording officer.

92
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,580
I was in charge of trying his case.

93
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,440
Deputy Magistrate Li,

94
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:10,720
what crime did he commit back then?

95
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,440
Theft.

96
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:16,200
Back then, a butcher shop was burglarized.

97
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:19,120
The owner of this butcher shop,

98
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:21,520
after finding his money vanished,

99
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:23,120
was burning with anxiety.

100
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,480
He immediately grabbed all the customers in the shop

101
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:27,880
and dragged them to the government office.

102
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,080
After some investigation,

103
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,960
I noticed this Moya.

104
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,560
His father

105
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:36,800
was a flying thief I personally arrested.

106
00:07:37,400 --> 00:07:41,040
As the saying goes, like father, like son.

107
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,920
In my heart, I was certain

108
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:48,320
that he most likely stole the money.

109
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:51,940
During the interrogation, he flatly denied it.

110
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:54,360
I found the stolen money on him

111
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:56,240
and threw him in jail.

112
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:57,880
I thought

113
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:01,120
it would make him turn over a new leaf.

114
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,880
Who knew

115
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,640
he wouldn't give up

116
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:07,440
and went back to his old ways.

117
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:09,800
In the end,

118
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,960
he actually dared to steal the Glazed Pearl.

119
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,280
Looking back now,

120
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:19,840
when he claimed in court that he was framed...

121
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:22,080
It's just an excuse.

122
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,410
What's more heartbreaking is that

123
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:26,520
after his daughter was born,

124
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:29,720
she also joined him in committing theft.

125
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:33,919
Now this father and daughter are guilty of many crimes.

126
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:37,600
The government has no choice but to offer a huge reward for their capture.

127
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:41,840
As they say, a thief's child can hardly change their thieving nature.

128
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:46,520
Unfortunately, the judgment made back then has come true.

129
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:50,440
Is the glazed pearl still in their hands?

130
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:54,600
We will only know that after we catch him.

131
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:59,460
When he committed the theft last time, whose house was robbed?

132
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:02,050
Feng Residence on the East Street.

133
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:06,800
This might be our breakthrough.

134
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,880
Mr. Su, go to the Feng Residence on the East Street.

135
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:11,560
Bring Shopkeeper Feng to the government office.

136
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:13,680
Let's ask him how he was targeted by Moya.

137
00:09:13,680 --> 00:09:14,880
Okay, I'm familiar with this family.

138
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:16,280
I'll go right away. Okay.

139
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,080
My lord.

140
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,880
My lord, I'll take my leave.

141
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,240
Be careful on the way.

142
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,840
Thank you for your hard work.

143
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,080
I am Feng Nan.

144
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,680
I usually do some silk business.

145
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,760
The money saved at home

146
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:32,080
is hard-earned money from doing business.

147
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,120
You see, it was all stolen by him.

148
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,960
I...

149
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,280
If you want your money back,

150
00:09:40,280 --> 00:09:42,360
answer my questions.

151
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:48,080
What did you just ask me?

152
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:50,800
Okay.

153
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,080
Think carefully.

154
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,440
Why are you hesitating?

155
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,240
Just say whatever comes to mind.

156
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:58,600
Well...

157
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,960
This...

158
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:07,680
How about this, if you don't want your money back...

159
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,720
We'll just take the ledger

160
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,760
and go home. Let's go.

161
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:12,680
Let's go.

162
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:18,400
The thief has already scouted the place anyway.

163
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,440
He'll come looking for you in a few months.

164
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,640
Let's go.

165
00:10:22,320 --> 00:10:23,480
Again?

166
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:24,960
What else?

167
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:29,480
To him, you're a long-term silver vault now.

168
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:31,400
Whenever he needs money,

169
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,920
he will come to you.

170
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:34,160
He'll keep

171
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,400
coming to you.

172
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,640
Okay, let's go.

173
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,920
Case closed. Time to go home.

174
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:40,960
Pack up.

175
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,560
We won't write this part. It's useless. Let's go first.

176
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:44,440
Pack all this up. Pack it up.

177
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:46,000
Pack it up. Wait.

178
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:48,640
I'll talk.

179
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:54,060
That was when he set his eyes on you in the jewelry store.

180
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:55,880
This one is pretty.

181
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,080
This one is pretty too.

182
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,440
Do you think I look good wearing this?

183
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:03,640
Yes.

184
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,880
Then I want all of these.

185
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:10,250
Thank you, boss. Let me give you a kiss.

186
00:11:10,560 --> 00:11:12,400
See if there is anything else you want.

187
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:13,560
Look over here.

188
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:18,160
Are you sure it was in the jade shop and not somewhere else?

189
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:20,800
Definitely.

190
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,200
Because during the robbery,

191
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:23,800
that woman also said it.

192
00:11:24,040 --> 00:11:25,200
Said what?

193
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:40,920
I didn't see anything.

194
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:45,200
Do you know how I targeted you?

195
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,240
He took a beautiful young woman

196
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:51,680
to the jade shop and bought several bracelets.

197
00:11:52,760 --> 00:11:53,760
What?

198
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,880
Look at you.

199
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,920
Working yourself to the bone to guard the little money the family has.

200
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:01,280
But what about him?

201
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,640
He spent all the family's money

202
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:04,800
on that mistress outside.

203
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:08,720
Do you think it's worth it being his wife?

204
00:12:09,520 --> 00:12:11,480
You went out with that woman again.

205
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:12,800
At a time like this,

206
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:14,800
why are you bringing this up?

207
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:16,240
You won't tell them?

208
00:12:16,280 --> 00:12:17,680
Then I will.

209
00:12:17,880 --> 00:12:20,360
All his money is hidden down the well in the courtyard.

210
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,240
Just pull the well rope,

211
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,700
and the money box comes up.

212
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,520
What do you mean by this?

213
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:26,120
I live frugally at home,

214
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:28,040
while you spend lavishly on a mistress.

215
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:29,640
Then no one gets to spend it.

216
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:33,760
Looks like they've been staking out the jade shop for a long time.

217
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:34,880
In that case,

218
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,560
I have an idea.

219
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:44,000
Young master,

220
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,920
you're so handsome. - Young master. - Yes.

221
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:49,200
Jinglan. Constable Su,

222
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,520
will this work?

223
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,560
This is his great idea,

224
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,400
luring the snake out of its hole.

225
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,320
My lady,

226
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:58,880
you could have done it,

227
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:01,200
but your face was seen by Black Crow.

228
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:03,320
So I had to hire three temporary ones.

229
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:05,890
Young master, you truly have heavenly looks.

230
00:13:06,560 --> 00:13:09,160
My lady, I paid to hire those three.

231
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,200
You have to reimburse me for this.

232
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:14,680
You have the nerve to ask me for money?

233
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:18,440
Young master, you're just too handsome.

234
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:19,520
Yes.

235
00:13:20,160 --> 00:13:21,440
Don't look, don't look.

236
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,600
I'm just looking.

237
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,440
Wow, so pretty.

238
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:27,160
Young Master, buy this for me.

239
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:28,600
Okay, I want this one.

240
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:29,720
Go pick.

241
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:32,960
Shopkeeper.

242
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,480
It's so beautiful.

243
00:13:34,560 --> 00:13:35,800
This one is pretty.

244
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:36,960
This one is pretty too.

245
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:39,880
Everything the three of them pick today,

246
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:40,880
I'll pay for it.

247
00:13:41,040 --> 00:13:41,760
Okay, boss.

248
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:43,640
So luxurious.

249
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,080
Do you like it?

250
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,040
I like it.

251
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:47,960
Buy some more.

252
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,520
So you finally came back.

253
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:07,250
Business has been too busy lately.

254
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:11,800
Rest early. I'm tired.

255
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,400
Will he take the bait?

256
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:25,200
He definitely will.

257
00:14:29,800 --> 00:14:32,040
If my father finds out about this...

258
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:38,120
Then I'd be the one going to jail.

259
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:00,720
Don't speak.

260
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:18,240
Young Master Liu,

261
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,600
it's time to get up.

262
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,760
It's an ambush. Let's split up.

263
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:35,160
Surround them! Catch the thieves!

264
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:16,400
If you don't want her to die now, step back!

265
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:22,960
Don't come any closer!

266
00:16:54,200 --> 00:16:56,640
Where is Mo Ya hiding?

267
00:16:59,400 --> 00:17:01,240
I don't know.

268
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,280
But I know

269
00:17:03,720 --> 00:17:05,119
your daughter

270
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:08,079
is suffering the same torture as me.

271
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:11,920
The pampered young lady,

272
00:17:12,319 --> 00:17:15,319
I don't know if she can bear it.

273
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:23,119
How dare you be so arrogant, you villain!

274
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:26,440
Just come at me with whatever you've got!

275
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:29,880
Let's see if your daughter dies first,

276
00:17:30,040 --> 00:17:31,800
or if I break first.

277
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,520
Speak up,

278
00:17:42,560 --> 00:17:45,560
or today will be your last day.

279
00:17:48,800 --> 00:17:50,440
Speak!

280
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:53,680
Mr. Su.

281
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:54,960
Deputy Magistrate Li has ordered,

282
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:56,620
no one is allowed in right now.

283
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:57,920
He's lost his mind.

284
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:00,120
Jueming!

285
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:02,340
Deputy Magistrate Li.

286
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:03,880
You can't do this!

287
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:04,960
What's going on?

288
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:06,800
Jinglan is in Mo Ya's hands.

289
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:08,400
If we hurt Mo Ying now,

290
00:18:08,480 --> 00:18:10,440
Jinglan will definitely be in greater danger.

291
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,600
We can't hurt her.

292
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:13,320
Yes.

293
00:18:13,360 --> 00:18:14,600
How dare he!

294
00:18:14,960 --> 00:18:17,820
If he dares to touch a single hair on Jinglan's head,

295
00:18:17,840 --> 00:18:20,120
I'll tear him to pieces!

296
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:25,400
I told you to find Mo Ya's hiding place.

297
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,200
Any results?

298
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:29,160
We have sealed off the entire Luoyang City.

299
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:30,560
He can't escape.

300
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:31,520
Besides,

301
00:18:31,560 --> 00:18:34,240
we have all the constables searching for him.

302
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:36,200
We absolutely cannot provoke Mo Ya,

303
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,920
or Jinglan will be in more danger.

304
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:39,640
Yes, Lord Li.

305
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:41,720
Search!

306
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:44,880
How long is it going to take?

307
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:47,840
Lord Li.

308
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:50,640
Jinglan is my daughter.

309
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:53,960
She is my only daughter.

310
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:56,440
Yes, Lord Li.

311
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:59,280
If Jinglan gets hurt in any way,

312
00:18:59,320 --> 00:19:00,160
you,

313
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:01,400
and you,

314
00:19:01,920 --> 00:19:04,000
will not have a good end.

315
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:05,280
Deputy Magistrate Li.

316
00:19:05,280 --> 00:19:05,740
Lord Li.

317
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:07,760
I have already given the order.

318
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:10,080
This woman has committed numerous crimes,

319
00:19:10,080 --> 00:19:12,360
including multiple severe thefts.

320
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:14,300
Her crimes are unpardonable.

321
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:16,520
What's more rampant,

322
00:19:16,560 --> 00:19:19,680
is that she dared to kidnap the daughter of a court official.

323
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:21,280
The evidence is conclusive.

324
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:23,240
Today at Shen hour,

325
00:19:23,360 --> 00:19:25,160
she will be beheaded.

326
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:28,580
Deputy Magistrate Li, you...

327
00:19:32,760 --> 00:19:34,040
Mo Ya.

328
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:37,000
Let's see if you come to save her,

329
00:19:37,560 --> 00:19:39,680
or not.

330
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:41,080
Boss, give me one.

331
00:19:41,080 --> 00:19:42,000
Here you go.

332
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:43,960
Crispy and savory sesame cakes!

333
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,640
Have one.

334
00:19:48,840 --> 00:19:49,800
Have one.

335
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:51,280
Coming.

336
00:19:51,560 --> 00:19:53,280
Crispy and savory sesame cakes!

337
00:19:53,280 --> 00:19:54,840
Have a sesame cake.

338
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:57,920
Here you go.

339
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,080
Thank you.

340
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:03,800
Have one too.

341
00:20:03,800 --> 00:20:06,240
Look at this. Quite the nerve.

342
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:07,280
Here you go.

343
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:10,560
This master thief is finally caught.

344
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:11,760
Yes.

345
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:12,800
I heard

346
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:14,560
it was a father-daughter duo.

347
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:16,880
But the mastermind hasn't been caught yet.

348
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:18,680
That's only a matter of time.

349
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:19,640
Right?

350
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:21,920
How long have these two been at large?

351
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:22,360
Shi Zhan Li Ru Chi Geng Duo.

352
00:20:22,360 --> 00:20:22,960
Shi Zhan Li Xiang Chi Geng Duo.

353
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:25,520
You have to trust the authorities.

354
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:27,360
Now that the young one is caught,

355
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:29,700
the older one definitely won't get away.

356
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:30,920
I don't think so.

357
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:32,480
Yeah, not necessarily.

358
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:25,920
With your little skills,

359
00:22:25,960 --> 00:22:27,240
you can't escape.

360
00:22:27,640 --> 00:22:28,640
Are you hungry?

361
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:31,400
I just bought some hot roast chicken and steamed buns.

362
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:32,760
Come eat some.

363
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:48,480
I might not be able to beat you,

364
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:49,880
but you stole the Liuli Orb.

365
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:51,080
You can't escape.

366
00:22:51,320 --> 00:22:53,050
I didn't plan to escape anyway.

367
00:22:53,120 --> 00:22:55,180
The city gates have long been sealed.

368
00:23:00,760 --> 00:23:02,800
There's still one who hasn't returned yet.

369
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:04,400
You want to take me hostage

370
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:06,080
as a bargaining chip.

371
00:23:08,040 --> 00:23:11,120
Li Ze issued a notice today.

372
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:14,960
Moying will be beheaded in public at the Shen hour.

373
00:23:15,520 --> 00:23:19,200
There are still two shichen left.

374
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:26,640
It seems

375
00:23:27,600 --> 00:23:29,930
you have no intention of saving her at all.

376
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:34,120
Don't you care if she lives or dies?

377
00:23:35,760 --> 00:23:37,760
I raised her myself.

378
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:41,820
We've been together day and night for years.

379
00:23:43,280 --> 00:23:45,080
How could I not care?

380
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:51,920
But she's your daughter.

381
00:23:54,160 --> 00:23:55,240
No matter what,

382
00:23:55,280 --> 00:23:56,920
I must leave today.

383
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:59,880
You are my daughter.

384
00:24:00,560 --> 00:24:02,620
What nonsense are you talking about?

385
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,880
I am not talking nonsense.

386
00:24:07,000 --> 00:24:09,360
Every word I say is true.

387
00:24:13,000 --> 00:24:15,320
is my daughter.

388
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:21,240
That year, your mother was several months pregnant.

389
00:24:21,720 --> 00:24:24,000
Every day after working at the grain shop,

390
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,200
I hurried home to take care of her.

391
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:27,960
Although life was poor,

392
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:30,720
thinking of the child in her womb

393
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:34,840
filled my heart with warmth and anticipation.

394
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:39,560
That day, I wanted to buy some meat to nourish your mother,

395
00:24:39,600 --> 00:24:42,640
so I went to the butcher shop.

396
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:44,160
But as soon as I arrived,

397
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:45,800
before I could even buy the meat,

398
00:24:45,800 --> 00:24:48,200
the butcher said some silver was missing

399
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:50,160
and claimed there was a thief in the shop.

400
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:52,760
We argued with him endlessly.

401
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:54,760
Just then, a constable came by.

402
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:57,280
We followed him to the magistrate's office

403
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:58,920
to seek justice.

404
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:03,360
Fellow villagers,

405
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:06,760
money was stolen from the butcher shop today,

406
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:08,080
causing a dispute

407
00:25:08,120 --> 00:25:09,600
that was brought to court.

408
00:25:09,720 --> 00:25:12,560
Unfortunately, the magistrate had to go out

409
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:14,200
on official business,

410
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:17,720
so he cannot try this case in person for now.

411
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:21,720
I am Li Ze, the Registrar.

412
00:25:21,920 --> 00:25:23,760
By the grace of the magistrate,

413
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:27,840
I will temporarily take charge of this case.

414
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:31,000
If you have anything to say,

415
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:32,640
please speak freely

416
00:25:32,760 --> 00:25:35,880
to help us investigate this case thoroughly.

417
00:25:46,360 --> 00:25:47,490
Court is in session.

418
00:25:48,120 --> 00:25:52,280
Justice.

419
00:25:55,520 --> 00:25:59,080
Sir, I put the money on the counter today.

420
00:25:59,120 --> 00:26:00,960
But when I turned around to get the meat,

421
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:02,600
all the money was gone.

422
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:05,000
Only they were present at the time.

423
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:07,200
The thief must be among them.

424
00:26:07,520 --> 00:26:09,360
This has nothing to do with me.

425
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:10,840
Nothing to do with me.

426
00:26:11,040 --> 00:26:12,440
Aren't you falsely accusing us?

427
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:14,770
How could it be with so many people around?

428
00:26:22,840 --> 00:26:26,320
I think I've seen you before.

429
00:26:26,920 --> 00:26:29,320
Is your father's name Zhang Ting?

430
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:30,400
Yes.

431
00:26:33,840 --> 00:26:35,440
What a coincidence.

432
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,320
Fellow townsfolk.

433
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:40,440
You may not know this.

434
00:26:40,840 --> 00:26:42,480
This man's father

435
00:26:42,760 --> 00:26:46,280
is a notorious thief.

436
00:26:49,360 --> 00:26:51,600
His father stole for years.

437
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:54,800
He was finally brought to justice by me.

438
00:26:56,000 --> 00:26:58,600
You were still young then.

439
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:02,560
You visited him in prison.

440
00:27:02,800 --> 00:27:05,080
We've met before.

441
00:27:06,080 --> 00:27:08,880
My Lord, that was over ten years ago.

442
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:12,200
It has nothing to do with the butcher shop incident today.

443
00:27:12,560 --> 00:27:15,000
Have these people been searched?

444
00:27:15,320 --> 00:27:17,760
Not yet, My Lord.

445
00:27:20,480 --> 00:27:21,320
Search him.

446
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:22,320
Wait.

447
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:24,760
You have no evidence. Why search me?

448
00:27:25,040 --> 00:27:26,720
My Lord, it was my father who broke the law back then.

449
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:27,760
He has already been punished.

450
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:28,960
I am a law-abiding citizen.

451
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:31,400
You can't just call me a thief based on his nonsense.

452
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:34,000
The villagers are watching. Zhang and Mrs. Li, they all know me.

453
00:27:34,000 --> 00:27:35,200
My Lord, give me justice.

454
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:37,000
All right.

455
00:27:37,280 --> 00:27:39,120
If you didn't steal it,

456
00:27:39,520 --> 00:27:41,480
why are you afraid of being searched?

457
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:42,280
Search.

458
00:27:44,120 --> 00:27:46,120
If you don't believe me, search me.

459
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:55,850
This is my family's money, My Lord.

460
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,800
My Lord, I found

461
00:28:02,840 --> 00:28:04,500
a hundred copper coins on him.

462
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:05,760
How much did you lose?

463
00:28:05,840 --> 00:28:06,840
A hundred coins.

464
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,080
It matches.

465
00:28:09,400 --> 00:28:11,860
My Lord, I am wrongly accused. I am innocent!

466
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:13,120
My wife is pregnant.

467
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:15,000
I wanted to buy some food for her at the butcher shop.

468
00:28:15,000 --> 00:28:16,720
This is all the money I've saved.

469
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:18,840
Look, my wife sewed this purse for me.

470
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,480
It still has a faint scent of jasmine.

471
00:28:20,480 --> 00:28:21,760
You can smell it.

472
00:28:21,800 --> 00:28:23,800
What a coincidence.

473
00:28:24,080 --> 00:28:25,560
Your father is a thief.

474
00:28:25,840 --> 00:28:27,200
You are also a thief.

475
00:28:27,560 --> 00:28:29,800
Dragons beget dragons, phoenixes beget phoenixes.

476
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:32,760
A thief's child will always be a thief.

477
00:28:33,120 --> 00:28:34,920
That's how he convicted me

478
00:28:34,960 --> 00:28:36,560
and threw me in jail.

479
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:39,600
But I didn't steal a single penny.

480
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:41,480
So I have a clear conscience.

481
00:28:41,800 --> 00:28:43,880
Because I had a hope in my heart,

482
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:46,840
which was my beloved wife

483
00:28:47,360 --> 00:28:49,160
and my soon-to-be-born child.

484
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:51,560
No matter how great the injustice and suffering,

485
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:52,800
I was not afraid.

486
00:28:52,840 --> 00:28:54,480
I could endure it all.

487
00:28:56,520 --> 00:28:57,680
Three months later,

488
00:28:57,840 --> 00:28:59,360
I was released.

489
00:29:08,000 --> 00:29:09,480
You're back.

490
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:18,520
How is my wife?

491
00:29:18,920 --> 00:29:20,480
Your wife

492
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:22,800
had a difficult labor.

493
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:26,720
She waited for you all night yesterday,

494
00:29:28,360 --> 00:29:30,880
but you never came.

495
00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:39,680
I'm sorry.

496
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:01,960
It's a girl.

497
00:30:03,040 --> 00:30:05,440
Look how cute she is.

498
00:30:09,280 --> 00:30:10,760
When I was released from prison,

499
00:30:10,760 --> 00:30:13,880
I happened to learn that Li Ze just had a baby girl.

500
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:18,320
Because of his prejudice that dragons beget dragons and phoenixes beget phoenixes,

501
00:30:18,320 --> 00:30:19,920
he falsely imprisoned me,

502
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:22,000
destroying my family.

503
00:30:24,200 --> 00:30:25,560
Since that is the case,

504
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:29,700
I will let him experience the consequences of his false words.

505
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:31,480
I stole his daughter

506
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:33,720
and sent my own daughter to his mansion.

507
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:35,600
I want to see

508
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:38,320
if his fallacy that a thief's child is always a thief

509
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:40,240
holds true.

510
00:30:45,160 --> 00:30:46,600
Nonsense.

511
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:50,360
Nonsense.

512
00:30:51,640 --> 00:30:53,240
Below your left chest,

513
00:30:53,280 --> 00:30:54,880
there is a red birthmark.

514
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:57,000
Besides your parents

515
00:30:57,360 --> 00:30:58,840
and the maid who serves you,

516
00:30:58,840 --> 00:31:00,760
I'm afraid no one else

517
00:31:00,840 --> 00:31:02,800
knows about this birthmark.

518
00:31:07,520 --> 00:31:09,120
Who would have thought

519
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,760
that the daughter of the great thief Mo Ya

520
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:13,520
would become the daughter of the Deputy Governor?

521
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:15,160
And became a coroner,

522
00:31:15,480 --> 00:31:17,810
and solved major cases one after another.

523
00:31:18,120 --> 00:31:19,650
Thinking about it this way,

524
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,720
aren't Li Ze's arrogant words from back then

525
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:26,000
especially ridiculous and absurd now?

526
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:31,400
You've been observing me for a long time.

527
00:31:32,280 --> 00:31:33,810
During the Ghost Festival,

528
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:36,000
when I was chasing you,

529
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:39,560
you already knew I was your daughter.

